{"id":232552078,"title":"教學：旋轉蠟筆再也不會用到一半縮進去啦！","content":"螢光筆滲到背面，紅筆又歪七扭八，只好買了旋轉蠟筆，結果畫一畫卻縮進去，是不是心很累>< 今天就來跟大家分享，如何自己DIY，零成本改造。廢話不多說，開始！\n( 1 ) 準備好你的筆\nhttps://i.imgur.com/zN1TkCO.jpg\n( 2 ) 將它拆解開來 ( 拆筆尾需用點力 )\nhttps://i.imgur.com/dHyPgCh.jpg\n( 3 ) 取一條膠帶，約與透明U型零件等長\nhttps://i.imgur.com/b8qDZaB.jpg\n( 4 ) 將膠帶黏貼在上 ( 要黏在U的外側哦 )\nhttps://i.imgur.com/SwrvQQA.jpg\n( 5 ) 用拇指、食指滑過，使膠帶服貼 ( 若膠帶稍微寬一點直接往U裡面黏即可 )\nhttps://i.imgur.com/Jr6PheR.jpg\n( 6 ) 登愣！大功告成 ~ 外表是看不出來的，試畫一下，感受自己努力的成果。\nhttps://i.imgur.com/Pfslg2b.jpg\n我個人是黏兩層膠帶，這樣的摩擦力個人最喜歡，原理很單純，就只是增加滑軌的摩擦力，讓畫線的時候能固定住，希望能幫上有一樣困擾的人哦！","excerpt":"螢光筆滲到背面，紅筆又歪七扭八，只好買了旋轉蠟筆，結果畫一畫卻縮進去，是不是心很累>< 今天就來跟大家分享，如何自己DIY，零成本改造。廢話不多說，開始！，（ 1 ） 準備好你的筆，（ 2 ） 將它拆","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"f74a0662-cb27-4d45-a6b7-7f87d3d02396","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-11-22T13:44:42.030Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-22T13:44:42.030Z","commentCount":6,"likeCount":84,"tags":[],"topics":["教學","文具","蠟筆","筆"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"文具","forumAlias":"stationery","school":"國立臺中科技大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":84}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/zN1TkCO.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/dHyPgCh.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/b8qDZaB.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/SwrvQQA.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/Jr6PheR.jpg"},{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/Pfslg2b.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"aee807e5-42d9-4269-b872-efe7fa0fff50","url":"https://i.imgur.com/zN1TkCOl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/zN1TkCOl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/zN1TkCOl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-11-22T13:44:42.030Z","updatedAt":"2019-11-22T13:44:42.